   CHANCELLOR Corp. (Boston) -- W. Barry Tanner resigned as
president and a director of this equipment-leasing firm.
Stephen C. Morison, vice chairman and chief executive
officer, will assume the duties of president. William C.
Sprong, senior vice president and treasurer, was named to
succeed Mr. Tanner as a director.
