STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
</IN>
<LP>
   The New York Stock Exchange said it will suspend trading
on the common stock of Schafer Value Trust Inc. before the
opening July 5.
   The closed-end investment fund declared a liquidating
distribution of $10.25 a share, payable July 5, to stock of
record Wednesday. As a result of the dividend, the market
value of the shares will be less than $5 million, the
exchange said.
</LP>
