</IN>
<LP>
   Tektronix Inc. said holders filed a class-action suit
against the company and certain of its officers and
directors, alleging violations of security laws.
   The suit, filed in federal district court in Portland,
Ore., accuses Tektronix of "withholding material adverse
information from the public" from July, 1989, to February,
1990. The electronics equipment maker didn't elaborate on the
lawsuit, calling it "entirely without merit."
